data.title: SpongeBob SquarePants: The Cosmic Shake
data.description: Join SpongeBob and his best friend Patrick in their usual mischief and meet all of your favorite Bikini Bottom characters from the television series.

data.title: AEW: Fight Forever
data.description: Experience the sensation of All Elite Wrestling in a game that combines nostalgic arcade-style matches with innovative tandem offensive moves.

data.title: Streets Of Rage 4
data.description: Clean up city streets in a beat ‘em up that features timeless gameplay with an electronic dance influenced soundtrack in a world filled with beautiful hand-drawn visuals.
